dialogue.name: AUGEBERT
dialogue.text: It's completed, Forename! The New Nest! Ain't it a thing of beauty?

dialogue.name: AUGEBERT
dialogue.text: We're makin' faster progress than I'd dared to hope, and it's thanks to good folk like yourself.

dialogue.name: AUGEBERT
dialogue.text: As you know, the area's to be a residential quarter for Ishgardians, with them as lost their homes in the war given priority.

dialogue.name: AUGEBERT
dialogue.text: That's ever been Francel's first objective in all thisâ”€makin' it so no more citizens are freezin' or starvin'.

dialogue.name: AUGEBERT
dialogue.text: Goes without sayin' that we'll keep on needin' supplies. So keep 'em comin', eh?
